### Update a lesson
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/lessons/{{lessonId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Programming Lesson",
  "description": "Updated description",
  "duration": 90,
